Fix #202. Tie date format 'auto' setting to system wide user preferences

There was a bug in the way the 'auto' flag attempted to find out
if the current local would require a 12 or 24 hour format. With this
change the 'auto' flag determines the format based on the users
system wide setting for the 12 or 24 format.
